{
  "texts": [
    "If it is not, we use the 'reasoning' prompt to generate an iCR to create a more accessible and naturally interactive conversational system.",
    "This can be seen in the architecture in Figure 2, denoted by (C).",
    "Unlike older dialogue systems, we interface with our core LLM using prompts.",
    "As mentioned in Section 3.3, we are using Vicuna-13b-v1.5.",
    "We provide the hospital information in a prompt with some additional guardrails, like \"you are not qualified to give any medical advice or make medical diagnoses\" and \"you do not have access to individual patient records or schedules\"."
  ]
}